    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 50-53.</p><p>Suppleness of Wind &amp; River</p><p>Beginning at 23rd level, you learn to step on air itself. You gain a fly speed equal to the speed gained by your Unarmored Movement feature (see Legendary Monk</p><p>table). In addition, your Unarmored Movement is increased by 10 feet, and again by another 10 feet when you reach 24th and 25th level.</p><p>In addition, whenever you gain a Fly speed greater than the speed granted by this feature, you can add your Unarmored Movement bonus to the new fly speed.</p></div>",
